data.description: Country living three bedroom two bath ranch located in Medina County close to route 18 and 71 and a part of the highly rated Highland School District.  Roof 2018, Septic Pumped March 2021. New Vinyl / LVT flooring throughout.  Whole house paint  You'll appreciate the spacious owner's suite with a private bathroom a bonus room off the owners suite . Imagine having an office, nursery or utilize your fitness equipment. Separated from the owners suite are 2 bedrooms with shared bathroom.  Bedrooms had all drywall, wiring, and insulation replaced.  The fireplace provides ambiance and warmth.  Your kitchen, with walls of cabinets to store all your culinary accessories. Take advantage of the banquet size dining room.  Entertain large, or small groups on an acre property.  Your neighborhood is a mix of new and classic homes.  Huge value living on an acre, in a neighborhood of big homes and part of the Highland School District.  Act now, come and see for yourself.   Call your Realtor to schedule your showing today.
